                        you via email in the future to tell you about OneBlood activities, opportunities to donate blood
                        in your area or changes to this privacy policy. We will not share your information with any
                        third party outside of our organization, other than as necessary to fulfill a request you make,
                        such as scheduling an appointment to give blood. Any other dissemination of information will
                        require your prior consent.
                    </p>
                    <div class="blood__label">
                        <h2 class="blood__h2">Information Collection</h2>
                        <p class="blood__p">
                            If you read or download information, we automatically collect and store:
                        </p>
