                            publication of this content as an endorsement by OneBlood of the views expressed herein, or
                            any warranty or guarantee of any strategy, recommendation, treatment, action, or application
                            of medication or preparation made by the author of the content.
                        </p>

                    </div>
                    <div class="blood__label">
                        <h2 class="blood__h2">Concerns? Complaints</h2>
